{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_02_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 3話 お兄ちゃん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……から揚げ定食と食後におしるこをください！\nあっ、ご飯は大盛りでお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… deep-fried chicken set meal and a red bean soup‚ please!\nOh‚ and a jumbo size for rice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "大盛り？　食べきれるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jumbo? You can finish all that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、大丈夫です！\n実は朝からずっと、お腹ペコペコで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yup‚ I’ll be fine!\nActually‚ my tummy’s rumbling ever since morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.01287228266398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 16.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "撮影が無事終わりましたから、食欲解禁です！\nあっ、このアイスも美味しそう～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But shooting finished without a hitch‚ so my appetite is off the leash!\nAhh‚ that ice cream looks yummy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いいけど、お腹を壊さない程度にしてくれよ\nいきなり沢山食べるのは、体によくないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s fine‚ but don’t eat so much you get indigestion.\nIt’s not good for your health to eat so much all of a sudden.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "くすっ、{user}さんって\n私の心配ばっかりしてませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really‚ {user}-san‚\ndo you never stop worrying about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Am I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 39.2333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ、今日のお仕事の前は\n過度なダイエットはするなよって毎日言ってましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true. Before today’s job‚ you were telling me every day\nnot to diet too hard‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "今だって私のお腹を心配してるじゃないですか\n他のみんなにもそんな風なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and now you’re worried about my digestion?\nAre you like that with everyone else too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 54.1666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、意識したことはなかったけど\n奥山さんには確かによく言ってるかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’ve never really thought about it.\nBut I might have been doing it more often to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "君はなんといってもまだ中学生だろ\n保護者目線になっているのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ you’re still in a middle school.\nMaybe I’m looking at you from a guardian’s perspective.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 68.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、{user}さん\n私のお父さんよりずっと若いですよね……うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ {user}-san‚\nbut you’re way younger than my dad… Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.07930488132295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "ということは――お兄ちゃん目線ですね！\nなんだか、いろいろと納得出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which means‚ you’re doing it from a Onii-chan’s perspective!\nA lot of stuff makes sense now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 84.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがお兄ちゃんみたい\nって、以前言ったのを覚えてますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re similar with my Onii-chan‚ {user}-san.\nDid you remember me saying that before?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.63634915351868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。見た目は似てないんだろ\nじゃあどこが似てるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. About not looking at all similar.\nSo what is similar?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 95.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "顔や声は全然違うんですけど、雰囲気というか……\n優しい空気感がそっくりなんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your faces and voices are totally different‚ but maybe there’s an aura about you…\nThe mood of kindness around you is exactly the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私、今日は\n落ち着いてお仕事が出来たんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why today I could\nrelax and get on with my job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.53333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……お兄さん、きっと君のことを\n凄く心配してるんだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m sure your Onii-chan\nworries about you a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.83004531860351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い妹が、東京と山形を行き来して\n手の届かないところで頑張ってるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because his cute sister is going back and forth between Tokyo and Yamagata‚\nand doing her best in a place he can’t reach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、可愛いなんて言われたこと\n一度もないですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha‚ he’s never called me\ncute before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "口にしないだけだと思う\n兄妹だと、照れて素直に言えないんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think maybe he just doesn’t say it out loud.\nIt’s embarrassing and hard for siblings to say directly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 129.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、星見プロのお兄ちゃんは\n今、言ってくれましたよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But my Onii-chan from Hoshimi Productions\njust said it‚ did he not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのお兄ちゃんって\n……俺？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your Hoshimi Productions Onii-chan…\nThat’s… me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 139.266666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　前からぼんやり思ってましたけど\n私がこっちにいる時のお兄ちゃんに任命します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep! I’ve been vaguely thinking that for a while‚\nbut I’m appointing you my Onii-chan for whenever I’m here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ダメですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No good?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 146.966666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと調子に乗り過ぎでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did I get carried away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
